{"tid":1053870,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖多小心眼睛疲勞]二月北歐+倫敦旅行相集","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T09:02:30.000Z","uid":36475,"like":31,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"11d017bb4dd6bd240585ac6b235162928eaad1ac","tid":1053870,"uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"重有一個學期就畢業(如無意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我係唔會有Gap year嘅人嚟<br />\n所以趁最後一個假期用晒啲里數一個人去一次歐洲旅行(第一次去咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n今次19日旅程遇到好多好人好事<br />\n雖然亦有好多唔好彩但總括而言都係一次好值得好開心嘅旅程<br />\n所有相都有執過同用Sony A7(第一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)影<br />\n鏡就FE 55mm F1.8 ZA 同 Voigtlander 15mm f/4.5 ver. I<br />\n我個人比較重手因為我主要係想將我當時嘅感受重現<br />\n色彩都係表達嘅一環所以唔寫實請見諒<br />\n因為用相表達為主所以我都唔多講只會標地名同可能有少少註解<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Norway In A Nutshell - 挪威縮影</span><br />\nClassic route, 由Oslo出發 &gt; Myrdal &gt; Fl&aring;m &gt; Bergen終點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7812/40126821473_ce4c50e710_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7812%2F40126821473_ce4c50e710_b.jpg&h=85dbbef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7847/33216545258_dd4f3149dc_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7847%2F33216545258_dd4f3149dc_b.jpg&h=1484d0df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7834/47039360212_a7ed5557ff_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7834%2F47039360212_a7ed5557ff_b.jpg&h=dd90ce40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7878/40126816083_11be354138_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7878%2F40126816083_11be354138_b.jpg&h=5aecc0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7870/33216530328_1e158f29e6_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7870%2F33216530328_1e158f29e6_b.jpg&h=19cff4c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7925/33216536728_713b13048f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7925%2F33216536728_713b13048f_b.jpg&h=ff5296f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中係Fl&aring;m住咗晚<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7927/40126812103_acdc5877d7_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7927%2F40126812103_acdc5877d7_b.jpg&h=d89b53c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7904/40126811403_70cea97b82_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7904%2F40126811403_70cea97b82_b.jpg&h=6e3b53c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7859/46177921175_ac3e0af23a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7859%2F46177921175_ac3e0af23a_b.jpg&h=e1180e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Oslo - 奧斯陸</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7848/46403605044_bf517289f9_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7848%2F46403605044_bf517289f9_b.jpg&h=f65ddb66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7802/33251906728_8626eb3db0_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7802%2F33251906728_8626eb3db0_b.jpg&h=4f73539a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7906/47127260481_7c738e9936_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7906%2F47127260481_7c738e9936_b.jpg&h=3e4eefc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7903/32185125607_ef6230a7e2_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7903%2F32185125607_ef6230a7e2_b.jpg&h=1f112817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Tromso - 特羅姆瑟</span><br />\n極光個到其實眼睇只係灰光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7849/40146641173_328a63a039_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7849%2F40146641173_328a63a039_b.jpg&h=dfaba0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7839/40146645833_e8b95fc5c3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7839%2F40146645833_e8b95fc5c3_b.jpg&h=b99d9e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7893/46387695484_7ea56dcaf3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7893%2F46387695484_7ea56dcaf3_b.jpg&h=b8bd939e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7878/46197484905_3a7e3568bf_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7878%2F46197484905_3a7e3568bf_b.jpg&h=f4da81eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7816/32169340737_712028619f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7816%2F32169340737_712028619f_b.jpg&h=fe37b03f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7864/32169341367_c7fccdb8f3_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7864%2F32169341367_c7fccdb8f3_b.jpg&h=1d00b248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Copenhagen - 哥本哈根</span><br />\nStunning, 一個將古今融合得好出色嘅城市<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7846/33189009978_0e2a39fe12_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7846%2F33189009978_0e2a39fe12_b.jpg&h=707cf1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7823/40099068963_418f2d716b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7823%2F40099068963_418f2d716b_b.jpg&h=00a81427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7872/32122223317_52c009a3a8_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7872%2F32122223317_52c009a3a8_b.jpg&h=e88d88e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7873/40099314953_9a50de09db_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7873%2F40099314953_9a50de09db_b.jpg&h=48e56418&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7850/32122398147_f224a25c3a_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7850%2F32122398147_f224a25c3a_b.jpg&h=12c6d9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7890/32122418517_88e2c9491f_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7890%2F32122418517_88e2c9491f_b.jpg&h=77c30203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7904/46340293484_808194b52b_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7904%2F46340293484_808194b52b_b.jpg&h=ac192a78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7864/46150505285_22e9ec4614_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffarm8.staticflickr.com%2F7864%2F46150505285_22e9ec4614_b.jpg&h=c5967980&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"